    <item>
      <title>沙特阿美的 120 亿美元问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-06-03/aramco-share-sale-saudis-ramp-up-pressure-on-wall-street-turkey-inflation-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯周日启动了沙特阿美 120 亿美元的二次发行，这项计划已经筹备多年。与沙特最近的股票发行一样，投资者在短短几个小时内就抢购了所有股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-06-03/aramco-share-sale-saudis-ramp-up-pressure-on-wall-street-turkey-inflation-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 13:52:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OPEC+ 计划恢复产量，布伦特原油价格跌至每桶 80 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/brent-oil-falls-to-80-a-barrel-as-opec-plans-to-restore-output</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于 OPEC+ 制定了逐步取消部分减产计划的时间表，布伦特原油价格自 2 月份以来首次跌破 80 美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/brent-oil-falls-to-80-a-barrel-as-opec-plans-to-restore-output</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 13:45:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Spotify 股价因美国股价上涨而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/spotify-shares-jump-on-us-price-increase</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大的流媒体音乐平台 Spotify Technology SA 宣布将在一年内第二次提高美国音乐价格，其股价周一大幅上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/spotify-shares-jump-on-us-price-increase</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 13:42:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>万豪首席执行官称美元正在推动出境游</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-03/marriott-ceo-says-dollar-is-driving-outbound-travel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[万豪国际集团首席执行官安东尼·卡普阿诺表示，美国的需求开始恢复正常。他还表示，美元走强正在推动美国出境游。他在“彭博监测”节目中发表了讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-03/marriott-ceo-says-dollar-is-driving-outbound-travel</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 13:34:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ChinaAMC CEO Yimei Li on ETF Inflows to China</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-03/chinaamc-ceo-yimei-li-on-etf-inflows-to-china-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华夏基金首席执行官李一梅在卡塔尔多哈举行的 2024 年 QEF 论坛期间接受彭博社记者哈斯琳达·阿明采访时，试图描绘出一幅乐观的 ETF 流入中国前景。她补充道：“国际参与者的加入给我们带来了压力，向我们展示了如何以国际化的方式做事，尤其是让投资者明白，我们可以将如此多不同的策略融入到这个行业中。我认为这是一件好事。”（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-03/chinaamc-ceo-yimei-li-on-etf-inflows-to-china-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 13:34:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚工会发起总罢工 电网、机场受损</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/nigerian-power-grid-airports-hit-as-unions-call-general-strike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚工会发起总罢工，导致国家电网关闭，并扰乱了这个西非国家主要机场的服务，周一尼日利亚出现大面积停电。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/nigerian-power-grid-airports-hit-as-unions-call-general-strike</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 12:34:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街策略师如何评价 Sheinbaum 在墨西哥的压倒性胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/investors-caught-off-guard-as-sweep-in-mexico-vote-tanks-peso</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有迹象表明克劳迪娅·谢恩鲍姆将以国会绝大多数优势就任总统，这导致墨西哥资产价格下跌，因为交易商担心新任领导人可能会获得立法支持以通过反市场改革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/investors-caught-off-guard-as-sweep-in-mexico-vote-tanks-peso</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 12:26:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯石油公司为备受争议的货物转运找到新地点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/russian-oil-finds-a-new-place-to-switch-in-the-mediterranean-sea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在希腊海军的压力下，俄罗斯石油贸易商在地中海找到了新的原油转运地点，这表明打击这一令监管机构和欧洲政府都感到震惊的活动将有多么困难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/russian-oil-finds-a-new-place-to-switch-in-the-mediterranean-sea</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 09:53:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
